---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="What is ManyTool | ManyTool" description="ManyTool 플랫폼 소개 및 사용 목적 안내 페이지입니다.">
  <Header />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black">What is ManyTool</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">ManyTool은 다양한 온라인 테스트와 도구를 제공하는 웹 기반 툴 플랫폼입니다.</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">ManyTool is a browser-based collection of practical utilities, casual games, interactive tests, and local map pages designed to be usable without sign-up.</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-slate-700">The goal of the site is not to publish empty landing pages, but to maintain individual pages that have a clear purpose, working functionality, and enough context for users to understand what each tool does.</p>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 text-slate-700">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900">What users can find here</h2>
      <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5">
        <li>Quick tools such as text counters, random pickers, roulette, and team splitters</li>
        <li>Interactive pages such as reaction tests, face shape tests, and casual browser games</li>
        <li>Map-based pages for fishbread shops, cafes, solo dining spots, and local restaurants</li>
        <li>AI-assisted utilities for image generation and commerce support workflows</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 text-slate-700">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900">Quality and ownership</h2>
      <p class="mt-2">Policy pages, contact details, and editorial rules are published so visitors and reviewers can understand how the site is maintained.</p>
      <p class="mt-2">Site issues, corrections, partnership requests, and policy-related questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:mooameensoo@gmail.com" class="font-medium text-slate-900 underline underline-offset-4">mooameensoo@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
